# MemeTools — Environment Variable Overview
#
# This root-level file is a pointer only. It contains no variables itself.
# Real environment templates live per application:
#
#   frontend/.env.example  — public (NEXT_PUBLIC_*) and frontend-only variables
#   backend/.env.example   — server-only variables (database, Supabase service role, port)
#
# No secrets are ever committed to this repository, in this file or any other,
# per docs/Phase-0.3-Technology-Stack-and-Development-Standards.md, Section 5 (Security Standards).
